{"title":"Marin Updates Nicasio 1 and Nicasio+, Adds Step-Thru Beyond Road Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/marin-updates-nicasio-1-plus-adds-step-thru-beyond-road-bike/","date":1729520883000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Marin Bikes)\" /></p>\n<p>It’s time for Marin Bikes to update its steel Boyond Road bikes: the Nicasio 1, and Nicasio+. In addition to those updates, Marin is also adding the all new Nicasio ST step-through. Marin says the Nicasio line of bikes is known for their endurance and versatility. The Nacasio+ supplies enhanced performance and comfort when the ride takes you on less-than-perfect roads.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio 1 and plus in action\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-and-plus-in-action-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Marin Bikes)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All of the new models are built using classic CroMo steel frames. The classic tubing offers the durability and comfort that is associated with steel frames.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio ST in action\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-in-action-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All of the bikes come with a plethora of mounts, and Marin’s Beyond Road geometry – geo that is made for any type of riding, long or short days, commuting, paved and unpaved roads, gravel roads… and well, you get the picture. The geo is supposed to be comfy-centric.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> Let’s take a gander. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Marin Nicasio 1</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $899</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio 1 full bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-full-bike-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-down-tube-braze-ons-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-down-tube-braze-ons-1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio 1 down tube braze ons\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-down-tube-braze-ons-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-down-tube-braze-ons-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-down-tube-braze-ons-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-down-tube-braze-ons-768x512.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-fork-mounts-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-fork-mounts-1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio 1 fork mounts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-fork-mounts-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-fork-mounts-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-fork-mounts-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-fork-mounts-768x512.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The best-selling Nicasio model first arrived on the scene in 2017. It’s proven to be a capable and affordable bike. It’s got a solid spec sheet with durable and dependable components. And the new Nicasio 1 now gets better tire clearance, coming speced with 38mm tires.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-1536x1024.webp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-seat-stay-bridge-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-front-hub-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-front-hub-1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio 1 front hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-front-hub-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-front-hub-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-front-hub-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-1-front-hub-768x512.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Series 1 double butted CrMo Beyond Road frame; clearance for up to 45mm tires</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano Claris 2×8 drivetrain, 11-32t cassette</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tektro road mechanical disc brakes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>WTB Exposure 700 x 36mm tires</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Available in two colors, black or bone grey</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Nicasio ST (the “ST” means “step-through”)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $899</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio ST full bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-full-bike-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio ST details\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-details-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio ST front fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-front-fork-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The newly added Nicasio “step-through” model features the dropped top tube making mounting and dismounting the bike easier. This step-through design can be particularly helpful when the bike is loaded with say, a child or cargo. It has the same frame construction and spec sheet carryover from the Nicasio 1….this one is just easier to throw a leg over. Or should I say, put a leg through?</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio ST steel tubes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-steel-tubes-1-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio ST seat tube logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-ST-seat-tube-logo-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Series 1 double butted CrMo Beyond Road frame; clearance for up to 45mm tires</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano Claris 2×8 drivetrain, 11-32t cassette</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tektro road mechanical disc brakes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>WTB Exposure 700 x 36mm tires</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Marin’s Nicasio+</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $1099</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio Plus full bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-full-bike-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio Plus rear derailleur\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-rear-derailleur-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Updated Nicasio Bikes Nicasio Plus Sword Black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-Updated-Nicasio-Bikes-Nicasio-Plus-Sword-Black-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Nicasio+ has been dubbed by Marin as “the Nic’ with a modern twist”. Although it shares the same frame construction as the Nicasio 1, the Nic’+ can fit large volume 650b x 47mm tires. It also sports the reliable and affordable 1×9 <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/microshift-sword-black-gravel-group/\" target=\"_blank\">microSHIFT Sword Black</a> gravel group.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/M